Name: Sky-mobi Ltd (ADR)
Description: DELISTED - Sky-mobi Limited (Sky-mobi) is a mobile application store in China. The Company operates mobile social games and provide applications and content with social network functions to its registered members. It focuses on the phone market in China. The Company collaborates with handset companies to pre-install Maopao on mobile handsets before shipment. Sky-mobi is positioned in China's mobile application ecosystem, which includes: users, which consists of younger age users; handset companies, including handset manufacturers and independent design houses; content providers, including application developers and content title owners, and payment service providers, including mobile service providers and other payment processing agents. On the Company's mobile application store, Maopao, users can browse, download and purchase a range of applications and content. On April 27, 2011, Sky-mobi launched of OPENSKY.
